Specification test_patterns

Patterns:
	pattern gt (a : int, b : int) returns (x : bool)
	let
		x = a > b
	tel
	
	pattern gt_0 (a : int) returns (x : bool)
	let
		x = gt(a,0)
	tel
	
	pattern gteq0 (a : int) returns (x : bool)
	var
		p1 : bool
		p2 : bool
	let
		x = gt_0(a) or (a == 0)
		
		p1 = x implies not (a < 0) 
		p2 = not (a < 0)
		
		--%PROPERTY p1
		--%PROPERTY p2
	tel	

Inputs:
	a : int
	b : int

Outputs:
	x : int
	y : int

Assumptions:
	a0 = gteq0(a)
	a1 = gt_0(b)

DerivedRequirements:
	dr0 = x >= a + 1
	dr1 = y >= b + 1

Requirements:
	p0 = x >= 1
	p1 = y > 1

